PSEUDOCODE FOR USERS SUM

set a maths random function to generate the two random integers between 1 and 100

store the first integer as integer1
store the second as integer2

prompt the user to provide the result to the sum of the two integers: integer1 and integer2

collect and store it as users_sum

check if the result is correct by using an if and else statement

if user_sum == integer1 + integer2:
    display "true"
else:
    display "false" 
